/>">
<span class="person">Alex Petralia</span> works in business analytics 
at an algorithmic trading firm in NYC. Prior to his work in finance, 
Alex was a data engineer at an e-commerce startup and a financial 
analyst at a management consulting firm.

Alex's work heavily integrates principles from software engineering 
into data analysis in order to help business analysts do their job 
better. He's passionate about all things data, from web scraping, 
distributed systems and data pipelines to data modeling, analysis and 
visualization. </p>
